BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313479056@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260312T162841Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T110000
SUMMARY:Mt Tabor 5k
DESCRIPTION:SlowPo Runners\nWe run around the large reservoir at the bottom (by the tennis courts)\, run up the long way by the now closed reservoir\, and then do a second loop around the raised reservoir. We run up one last hill to the top\, and then down down down! It's slightly over 5k (3 miles)\; pace adjusted for the group.\n\n[ https://www.strava.com/routes/4887546 ]\n[ https://www.portlandoregon.gov/parks/finder/index.cfm?action=ViewPark&PropertyID=275 ]\n\nAddress where we meet up is right next to 6220 SE Salmon St.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/slowpo-runners/events/313479056/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260222T185053Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260222T185053Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/2/2/a/5/600_483428869.jpeg
END:VEVENT
